---
import Cloud from "./icons/Cloud.astro"
---

<div class="space-y-8">
    <!-- Introducción -->
    <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <p class="text-lg text-white/90 leading-relaxed">
            Diseño <span class="text-cyan-400 font-semibold">arquitecturas escalables</span> segmentadas por entornos 
            (QA/Prod), optimizadas en <span class="text-yellow-400 font-semibold">costo</span> y 
            <span class="text-green-400 font-semibold">resilientes</span> mediante estrategias de branching y migración automatizada.
        </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Diagrama de Arquitectura -->
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-white/5 to-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/20 rounded-2xl p-8 hover:border-cyan-500/50 transition-all duration-300">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-cyan-400 mb-6 text-center">Mi Stack de Arquitectura Típica</h3>
        
        <!-- Diagrama ASCII mejorado -->
        <div class="font-mono text-sm text-white/80 overflow-x-auto">
            <pre class="text-center leading-relaxed">
<span class="text-blue-400">┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────┐</span>
<span class="text-blue-400">│</span>  <span class="text-cyan-300 font-bold">FRONTEND</span> (React/Next.js + TanStack Query)  <span class="text-blue-400">│</span>
<span class="text-blue-400">└─────────────────┬───────────────────────────────┘</span>
                  <span class="text-yellow-400">│</span> HTTPS/REST
                  <span class="text-yellow-400">▼</span>
<span class="text-yellow-400">┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────┐</span>
<span class="text-yellow-400">│</span>         <span class="text-yellow-300 font-bold">API GATEWAY / BACKEND</span>             <span class="text-yellow-400">│</span>
<span class="text-yellow-400">│</span>          <span class="text-white/70">(NestJS + Prisma ORM)</span>              <span class="text-yellow-400">│</span>
<span class="text-yellow-400">└──────┬──────────────────────────────┬─────────┘</span>
       <span class="text-green-400">│</span>                              <span class="text-purple-400">│</span>
       <span class="text-green-400">│</span> Auth                         <span class="text-purple-400">│</span> Files
       <span class="text-green-400">▼</span>                              <span class="text-purple-400">▼</span>
<span class="text-green-400">┌──────────────┐</span>              <span class="text-purple-400">┌──────────────┐</span>
<span class="text-green-400">│</span> <span class="text-green-300 font-bold">MS Entra ID</span> <span class="text-green-400">│</span>              <span class="text-purple-400">│</span> <span class="text-purple-300 font-bold">Cloudflare</span> <span class="text-purple-400">│</span>
<span class="text-green-400">│</span> <span class="text-white/60">(OAuth 2.0)</span>  <span class="text-green-400">│</span>              <span class="text-purple-400">│</span> <span class="text-white/60">R2 Storage</span>  <span class="text-purple-400">│</span>
<span class="text-green-400">└──────────────┘</span>              <span class="text-purple-400">└──────────────┘</span>
       
       <span class="text-cyan-400">│</span> DB Connection
       <span class="text-cyan-400">▼</span>
<span class="text-cyan-400">┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────┐</span>
<span class="text-cyan-400">│</span>      <span class="text-cyan-300 font-bold">DATABASE (PostgreSQL + Neon)</span>         <span class="text-cyan-400">│</span>
<span class="text-cyan-400">│</span>  <span class="text-white/60">• Branching por entorno (QA/Prod)</span>         <span class="text-cyan-400">│</span>
<span class="text-cyan-400">│</span>  <span class="text-white/60">• Migraciones automáticas (Prisma)</span>        <span class="text-cyan-400">│</span>
<span class="text-cyan-400">└─────────────────────────────────────────────────┘</span>

       <span class="text-red-400">│</span> Deployment
       <span class="text-red-400">▼</span>
<span class="text-red-400">┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────┐</span>
<span class="text-red-400">│</span>         <span class="text-red-300 font-bold">INFRAESTRUCTURA (Cloud Run)</span>        <span class="text-red-400">│</span>
<span class="text-red-400">│</span>  <span class="text-white/60">• Despliegue aislado por servicio</span>         <span class="text-red-400">│</span>
<span class="text-red-400">│</span>  <span class="text-white/60">• CI/CD automatizado</span>                      <span class="text-red-400">│</span>
<span class="text-red-400">│</span>  <span class="text-white/60">• Costo optimizado (~CLP 1.6k/día)</span>        <span class="text-red-400">│</span>
<span class="text-red-400">└─────────────────────────────────────────────────┘</span>
            </pre>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Principios de Arquitectura -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/10 rounded-xl p-6 hover:border-yellow-500/50 transition-all hover:scale-105">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
                <div class="bg-yellow-500/20 p-2 rounded-lg">
                    <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-yellow-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1"></path>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-yellow-400">Optimización de Costos</h4>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm text-white/70">
                Cloud Run sin instancias mínimas. Escalado bajo demanda real. Monitoreo constante de recursos.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/10 rounded-xl p-6 hover:border-cyan-500/50 transition-all hover:scale-105">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
                <div class="bg-cyan-500/20 p-2 rounded-lg">
                    <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-cyan-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z"></path>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-cyan-400">Seguridad Empresarial</h4>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm text-white/70">
                Autenticación OAuth 2.0 con MS Entra ID. Segmentación de roles. Gestión granular de permisos.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/10 rounded-xl p-6 hover:border-green-500/50 transition-all hover:scale-105">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
                <div class="bg-green-500/20 p-2 rounded-lg">
                    <Cloud class="w-6 h-6 text-green-400" />
                </div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-green-400">Escalabilidad Real</h4>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm text-white/70">
                Neon branching para QA/Prod. Migraciones sin downtime. Infraestructura que crece con el negocio.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Casos de uso reales -->
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-500/10 via-purple-500/10 to-yellow-500/10 border border-white/20 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-cyan-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
            </svg>
            Aplicado en producción
        </h4>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-white/80">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-cyan-400 mt-1">▸</span>
                <span><strong>Sistemas marítimo-logísticos:</strong> Koralis/Remoras - Gestión de cotizaciones y operaciones con trazabilidad completa</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-yellow-400 mt-1">▸</span>
                <span><strong>Gestión documental:</strong> Integración con OneDrive y Microsoft Graph API para cafetería Panichini</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-green-400 mt-1">▸</span>
                <span><strong>Plataformas multi-entorno:</strong> 4 ambientes separados (Dev, QA, Staging, Prod) en Sotex</span>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</div>
